column5: Would like to wordsmith this post but with the combination of frigid ice making temps and inhaling 2 stroke fumes from trolling all day I'm still groggy and a bit dazed so I'll let the vid do the talking. Happy New Year everyone.
Good stuff Man! Thanks for sharing. Looks cold out there.

Good stuff Man! Thanks for sharing. Looks cold out there. The morning started with feeling like -19 but as winds calmed and the sun stretched out as high as it could for this time of year it was actually nice out.
Some sweet fish there! Good job on the video as well, I live in Quinte and have yet to get out the falls/winter this year.... Damn work and overtime.  Congrats on a successful outing.  G

Some sweet fish there! Good job on the video as well, I live in Quinte and have yet to get out the falls/winter this year.... Damn work and overtime.  Congrats on a successful outing.  G Thanks Gerritt but I tell ya if the drive wasn't such a killer I'd be up there fishing all year long for every species there is to offer. It truly is an Anglers paradise.
